Nat Carr https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nat_Carr 0 Nat Carr (August 12, 1886 - July 6, 1944) was an American character actor of the silent and early talking picture eras. During his eighteen-year career, Carr appeared in over 100 films, most of them features.
